      "content": "but a counselor can't fix this. they just give you these scripts and tell you it gets better, but it won't. the world has already decided who i am. i'm a cautionary tale now, not a person. honestly, sometimes it feels like the most logical thing to do is just stop fighting a battle that's already been lost. it feels like the only way to actually get some peace from the shame.",
